{"tid":1461301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣招募］青衣人站起來，加入青衣文宣！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:17:09.000Z","uid":199622,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5a84e25a62debafc9e8e5810ac66a693dba44c","tid":1461301,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"（代人出post)<br />\n<br />\n各位手足你好，我們是青衣文宣，主要專注於青衣的宣傳工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=61fd50c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們是一群為了令運動繼續保留溫度而聚在一起的人，從而令政府不能逃避問責的責任。<br />\n<br />\n運動發展至今，政府仍未回應訴求，很多香港人都感到無力， 甚至憤怒。但我們已沒有退讓的餘地，沒有放棄的成本，只能有一起對準目標，因為政府有無數施政欺壓平民。<br />\n<br />\n如果你懷著相同理念，想出多一分力，行多一小步。 我們現在誠意邀請你加入我們。<br />\n<br />\n經過好多人幫手，開左兩次post 之後，我哋而已經開到3次傳單團，分別係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日<br />\n18號<br />\n21號</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果要keep住做更多嘅事，如banner or 放映會，就真係好需要人力幫手。，所以我哋喺度想招募三種人才：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">活躍的天才</span></span><br />\n有心、發表建設性意見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">超級設計師</span></span><br />\n其實唔洗好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋好多人都係自學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有經驗的老屎忽</span></span><br />\n因為小弟不才，無搞過放映會既經驗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=61fd50c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n其實青衣有好大個連儂牆（其實係橋先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 仲有好多空間做到更加多嘅嘢，大家可以一齊發表下唔同睇法👀🧠 <br />\n<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;💻歡迎加入👩🏼&zwj;💻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=61fd50c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Umuektn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmuektn.jpg&h=638ab841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d85f00ad5ad20725733445a1f1448680b8e55fae","tid":1461301,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"91386b25940d8b4757a8de5bdbe2378124f72660","tid":1461301,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"873e29fe84e0168baede70ded028255b08231782","tid":1461301,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"229985bcee7d037062795fda988eb45a529760a2","tid":1461301,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0c15ffac56575242bc293ef777c0cc9397f37dea","tid":1461301,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"21c3ea0d197a87a7d75ae2